Quick Summary

  Allowed:
  - Calling xlibs functions from your mod (intended use, no restrictions)
  - Use in modpacks (encouraged)
  - Addons, patches, integrations
  - Personal use and configuration

  Required:
  - Visible credit if copying code: xlibs by Damian Sirbu

  Not allowed:
  - Copying code without credit
  - Competing utility libraries that replicate xlibs modules

